code: @Override public FloatType getRandom(Random rnd) {     return new FloatType(rnd.nextFloat()). }
@Override public void write(DataOutputView out) throws IOException {     out.writeFloat(this.value). }
@Override public void read(DataInputView in) throws IOException {     this.value = in.readFloat(). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj instanceof FloatType) {         FloatType other = (FloatType) obj.         return Float.floatToIntBits(this.value) == Float.floatToIntBits(other.value).     } else {         return false.     } }
